When the crooks undressed their victim, they wiped him away from everyone and a line of bandits stood around so that no one could hear, see or help anything. Now this is how "open" court hearings are held in a prison. So that the fly does not fly and the word does not fly out. The bandits, as they dreamed of in the 90s, grew up in the scale of their activities and firmly entrenched themselves in the Kremlin, the court and the Duma.